snippet: Coach Nick Saban expects a lot from the Crimson Tide linemen and linebackers, and the last thing they want to do is disappoint him.
abstract: Alabama head football coach Nick Saban expects a lot from his defense, and his players do not want to disappoint; top-ranked Alabama is on track to win its third championship in four years.
lead_paragraph: Coach Nick Saban expects a lot from the Crimson Tide linemen and linebackers, and the last thing they want to do is disappoint him.

headline.seo: Alabama Defense Fears but One Man: Nick Saban
